This drink is very easy to drink and very inoffensive. Tastes like water with a distant echo
of orange citrus. Somewhat bitter. If this marketed as an energy drink, I'd be
upset, because it's none of the things energy drinks are, even the
non-carbonated ones. But, as a drink that happens to have caffeine, it's
pleasant, cheap, and does have some sugar but not too much.

